u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/27\/ahl-al-iman-restrained-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":1978,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Bloodshed: Believers are most hesitant to kill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most hesitant of people in killing are the people of faith.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2666 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut Al-San'ani said, \"The meaning is that most people who avoid killing are the believers, because\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9662,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/iman-never-combined\/","url_meta":{"origin":1978,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hasad: Faith and envy never coexist in heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFaith and envy are not combined within a believing servant.\" Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3109 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\